name: RWKV-LM
description: RWKV v2 is a RNN with transformer performance. It can be directly trained like a GPT transformer (parallelizable). You only need x_t, a_t, b_t of position t to compute the vectors for position t+1. Hence it can be 100x faster than GPT, and 100x more VRAM friendly, and you get a free sentence embedding.
